# Editor workspace posture

**NOT ALLOWED** to regress [`.vscode/settings.json`](../../.vscode/settings.json) in ways that break formatting, stall the file explorer, or re-scan the whole monorepo.

SSOT: [`scripts/lib/editor-posture.mjs`](../../scripts/lib/editor-posture.mjs) · gate: `pnpm check:editor-biome` · hook: [`.cursor/hooks/no-editor-biome-drift.mjs`](../hooks/no-editor-biome-drift.mjs)

## Biome (format + LSP)

| Setting | Value |
|---------|-------|
| `biome.lsp.bin` | Platform map → native `@biomejs/cli-*` (not node wrapper) |
| `biome.configurationPath` | `"./biome.jsonc"` |
| `biome.lsp.watcher.kind` | `"none"` |
| Product JS/TS/JSON/CSS | `"editor.defaultFormatter": "biomejs.biome"` |
| Markdown/MDX | Prettier only |

Requires [`.npmrc`](../../.npmrc) `public-hoist-pattern[]=@biomejs/cli-*` + `pnpm install`.

## TypeScript (tsserver)

Per-package `Initializing …/tsconfig.json` is **normal once per package per session** (37 package tsconfigs). Reduce repeat cost:

| Setting | Value |
|---------|-------|
| `typescript.disableAutomaticTypeAcquisition` | `true` |
| `typescript.tsserver.maxTsServerMemory` | `8192` |
| `typescript.tsserver.experimental.enableProjectDiagnostics` | `false` |
| `typescript.preferences.includePackageJsonAutoImports` | `"off"` |
| `typescript.tsserver.useSyntaxServer` | `"auto"` |
| `typescript.tsserver.watchOptions.excludeDirectories` | includes `docs-V2`, build trees |

## Explorer / watchers

| Rule | Detail |
|------|--------|
| `explorer.excludeGitIgnore` | **false** — use explicit excludes |
| `files.exclude` | Build artifacts + `.cursor` / `.agents` (not `docs-V2`) |
| `files.watcherExclude` | SSOT list incl. `docs-V2/**` watcher-only, drizzle, shadcn-studio, `.pnpm` |

## Tailwind extension

| Setting | Value |
|---------|-------|
| `tailwindCSS.experimental.configFile` | `apps/web/postcss.config.mjs` |
| `tailwindCSS.files.exclude` | Heavy trees (docs-V2, drizzle, e2e, agent trees) |

## User settings

User-level Cursor/VS Code settings must **not** override workspace: `explorer.excludeGitIgnore: true`, global Biome node-wrapper paths, ESLint as TS formatter.

## Verify

```bash
pnpm check:editor-biome
node --test scripts/check-editor-biome-hook.test.mjs
```

